          style="width:120px;height:60px;">
      </a>

      <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 11px"> ABC Company | Meisenweg 27 | 67665
        Kaiserslautern | Germany<br />
        <b>E </b><a href=" #">support@abc.com</a> | <b>P </b>+49 179 2822 944 | </p>

